### Memory Commit

```jac
with entry {
    # Commit memory to database
    commit();
}
```

```python
from jaclang.lib import Node, Walker, spawn, root, on_entry

class Task(Node):
    title: str
    done: bool = False

class TaskFinder(Walker):
    @on_entry
    def find(self, here: Task) -> None:
        print(f"Found: {here.title}")

spawn(TaskFinder(), root())
```
